                            <comment id="282659" author="ofaaland" created="Mon, 19 Oct 2020 23:33:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Jian, thanks for figuring that out.&#160; I didn&apos;t look closely enough.&#160; Can RHEL 7.9 build be enabled for b2_10?&#160; Or is that problematic?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
